So it seems that the cat has left the bag! Yes it is true I had surgery and I am so happy I choose to do so!! 
.
.
.
December 15, 2022 I went under the knife and had breast augmentation done and to be honest it was my first surgery ever so I was a bit nervous since it was the first time. For months I had to search for a Doctor Who was not only amazing at what he did and knowledgeable but also had certification and experience. I wanted to see his previous Work to show what he had done in his past. I first heard of Dr Gerth through another model who got much more work done and she looked flawless. From the moment I met the doctor I knew I had made the right decision. And the process was extremely easy. I went in there. I told him what I wanted. I heard their opinions I heard their advice. I was ready for this new chapter in my life quickly left a deposit. I was open to changing my life and now, three months post operation. I am the happiest I’ve ever been. I feel the happiest. Not only has my confidence skyrocket, but life has just been a little bit more easier because I did something for me. It’s very important to live life for you and no one else. 
.
.
Do not worry about what anyone else has to say or what they think about you. It takes courage to want to be different. ❤️ if you have questions in regards to my surgery send me a DM If you want to inquire about pricing send me a DM and I’ll get you in contact with their office or you can call them directly at 305-204-6183
.
.
.
Here’s a video of transition of the first three months after surgery so you can see the healing process. Everyone’s results are always different but at the end of the day when healing, it is very important that you truly make time to heal properly. 
.
